This meta-analysis is the latest one to evaluate the
efficacy and safety of MI-TLIF and O-TLIF for
single-level degenerative lumbar diseases and to de-
termine which surgical technique is superior. A few
studies [12, 13] have described a superior or com-
parative outcome for patients undergoing MI-TLIF
approach for single-level degenerative lumbar
diseases. Singh et al. [11] showed MI-TLIF demon-
